# Logistic Regression

# Objective
Build a binary classification model using Logistic Regression.

# Dataset
Breast Cancer Wisconsin Dataset
link - https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/breast-cancer-wisconsin-data

# Steps Performed
- Data Cleaning
- Feature Scaling
- Train-Test Split
- Model Training
- Evaluation (Confusion Matrix, ROC-AUC)

# Results
- High Accuracy
- Strong ROC-AUC Score

# Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

# Outputs
- Confusion Matrix
- ROC Curve
